            "title": "盤中速報 - 櫃買市場加權指數下跌-4.97點至243.74點，跌幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間28日10:36，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.97點（或2%），暫報243.74點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-2.26%</li><li>近 1 月：-4.31%</li><li>近 3 月：-2.89%</li><li>近 6 月：-8%</li><li>今年以來：-2.79%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>車用二極體概念領跌-4.37%。其中    台半(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5425-TW</a>)            下跌        5.75%            ;        朋程(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8255:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8255\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8255-TW</a>)            下跌        4.58%            ;        虹揚-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6573:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6573\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6573-TW</a>)            下跌        3.85%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>人臉辨識概念領跌-3.60%。其中    鈺創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5351-TW</a>)            下跌        5.85%            ;        新唐(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4919-TW</a>)            下跌        5.3%            ;        華晶科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3059-TW</a>)            下跌        5.05%    。</p></section></main>",
